WAVE ENERGY

wave_energy is the energy channel of the qu-septit native compute substrate
in fadriel_phase2, the seven universal properties are made explicit as seven wave channels that interact through the 21 pairwise couplings
wave_energy carries the energy property: how much of a body's pilot light is currently lit
it interacts with the other six channels (phase, spin, charge, coherence, coupling, observer) to produce the body's full state evolution

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe fadriel_phase2.zc
observe wave_phase.rana

the 7 properties of wave_energy itself:
1 ENERGY one: this channel holds energy primarily
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING half: present in all pairwise interactions but not maximal in any
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB carry_energy
hold the energy property of every body in the sea
each body's current energy is one cell in this channel

VERB exchange_with_others
participate in the 21 pairwise interactions where energy plays a role
energy couples to phase via the wave equation, to coupling via the bond strength formula, to observer via decoherence

a channel is not a variable
a channel is one of seven dimensions of the body's living state
together with the other six it constitutes the full physics of the body's evolution
